Products.Name: Swim suit top
Products.Subtitle: A glamorous swim suit top
Products.Description: Bring a little glamour to the deck or the dock. Our Beach Club collection is sure to turn heads with rich colors and chic details. Bikini Top has a flattering sweetheart neckline with removable straps to create a different look (and to prevent tan lines). 74% nylon/26% spandex. Hand wash. Imported.

Products.Name: Swim suit bottom
Products.Subtitle: The perfect swim suit bottom
Products.Description: A cheeky bikini bottom featuring a vibrant floral print and ruffle trim. Elasticized trim. Fully lined. Minimal coverage. Knit. Machine wash cold, dry flat. Imported.

Products.Name: High heel shoes
Products.Subtitle: A great pair of shoes
Products.Description: Reach new heights of style in Rachel Zoe's skyscraper platform sandals, with retro-now styling that will work with all your day and night faves. Imported.

Products.Name: Green beads necklace
Products.Subtitle: The necklace that goes with everything
Products.Description: Green bead necklace. 10 stranded pearl necklace with silver colour decorative bead detail. Add a bit of colour to any outfit with this necklace.

Products.Name: Blue stone necklace
Products.Subtitle: The necklace that goes with everything
Products.Description: Ever so elegant and feminine, this double strand of fine emerald beads with diamond clasp is amazing. Over 190 carats of fine bright faceted emerald green beads strung beautifully with an exquisite ‘bow’ style 18k white gold clasp with over a third of a carat of diamonds.

Products.Name: Red beads necklace
Products.Subtitle: The necklace that goes with everything
Products.Description: Give your style a personality and attitude with this exotic tropical surfer necklace. Hand-crafted white puka shell chip beads, barrel style clasp.
